#: ../../../modules/vtk-modules/Rendering/OpenVR/README.md:29
msgid ""
"The VTK `OpenVR` module is considered legacy and not under active "
"development. Please see the VTK `OpenXR` module for support for additional "
"controllers and alternate input mechanisms."
msgstr ""

